{
  "stem": "22047.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we were discussing the business of the man getting hit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that was actually after-- afterwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had-- we had fought for several days in the outpost, and then we pulled back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so really, the elements, the-- the severity of the attack by the Germans, had subsided somewhat in our area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were still pushing like mad toward Belgium, trying to break through to the sea to split our forces.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this happened to be-- we were in this-- actually, I was-- our-- our battalion was in corps reserve.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What we were doing was, as I think I earlier mentioned, digging foxholes around the rear to prevent an attack.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If we-- a pending attack would come, we would occupy those holes and fight off any attack by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well this one day-- and I-- I talked a little bit about it-- I was standing there, and this tank across the valley had been shooting rounds from its gun-- a 88-millimeter gun-- into the city of Schonenberg and trying to-- just harassing fire is what it was.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they saw this-- it happened to be Lloyd [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Gee ?] was his name-- Sergeant [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Gee-- ?] was supervising the digging of holes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this round hit right next to him and, of course, killed him instantly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went running down there to see what had happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I saw that, of course, he was dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And as I think I mentioned earlier, one of your people is killed, it's like a member of the family being killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the States, this fella and his brother, they were a set of twins.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
